### New App
POST http://localhost:3000/cteapi/v1/apps
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "GOORIIs Store"
}

### Tes Transaksi In
POST http://localhost:3000/cteapi/v1/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: app_bb7c9b319f31397f493074e5fad15151

{
  "type": "IN",
  "category": "SALES",
  "amount": "1000",
  "paymentMethod": "CASH",
  "description": "Tes transaksi 1."
}

